OL,3,CGaza: British families call for
OL,4,CUkrainian-style visa scheme to get
OL,5,Crelatives out
OL,7,FBritish families and campaigners are
OL,8,Fcalling on the Home Office to
OL,9,Fintroduce a Ukrainian-style visa
OL,10,Fscheme to help get their loved ones
OL,11,Fout of Gaza, as the war continues to
OL,12,Frage on.
OL,14,FShahd Abusalama, a British citizen who
OL,15,Ffirst came to the UK in 2014, told ITV
OL,16,FNews she feels "abandoned" by the
OL,17,Fgovernment despite her numerous
OL,18,Fappeals to get her extended family out
OL,19,Fof Gaza.
