OL,5,Crelatives out
OL,7,FA visa scheme to help with this, she
OL,8,Fsays, is "long overdue" as her
OL,9,Fextended family - dispersed in the
OL,10,Fsouth and north of the territory - are
OL,11,Ffaced with starvation and a constant
OL,12,Fbarrage of Israeli missiles.
OL,14,FHer family home has already been
OL,15,F"bombed and burned down" while in
OL,16,FOctober 2023, a bomb killed 22 of her
OL,17,Fextended family and friends in their
OL,18,Fhome.
