OL,3,CGaza: British families call for
OL,4,CUkrainian-style visa scheme to get
OL,5,Crelatives out
OL,7,F"We need to have the choice to bring
OL,8,Four families home and save them until
OL,9,Fthe bombs stop falling - even if it is
OL,10,Fjust temporary. We are just asking the
OL,11,FHome Office to treat Palestinians as
OL,12,Fhumans," she says.
OL,14,FMore than 70 charities, law firms, and
OL,15,Forganisations sent a letter to Home
OL,16,FSecretary James Cleverly on Tuesday,
OL,17,Fin which they claim existing
OL,18,Fimmigration routes out of Gaza "are
OL,19,Finsufficient and not working".
