OL,7,F"Unlike in the case of British
OL,8,Fnationals, for whom the British
OL,9,Fgovernment has facilitated evacuation
OL,10,Fto Egypt, the British government is
OL,11,Fnot facilitating safe passage for
OL,12,FPalestinians in Gaza seeking to
OL,13,Freunite with their family members in
OL,14,Fthe UK," the letter says.
