OL,3,CGaza: British families call for
OL,4,CUkrainian-style visa scheme to get
OL,5,Crelatives out
OL,7,FUnder the current system, Palestinians
OL,8,Fneed to submit their biometric data to
OL,9,Ffile an immigration application to the
OL,10,FUK, but the only visa application
OL,11,Fcentres are in neighbouring Egypt,
OL,12,Fwhich charges exorbitant fees to allow
OL,13,FPalestinians to exit the Strip.
OL,15,FSignatories of the letter - campaign-
OL,16,F include the Refugee Council,
OL,17,FCare4Calais and the Helen Bamber
OL,18,FFoundation as well as law firms
OL,19,FBirnberg Peirce and Duncan Lewis.
