OL,7,FA spokesperson for the Home Office did
OL,8,Fnot respond to ITV News' request for
OL,9,Fcomment, but the department previously
OL,10,Fit has no plans to establish a
OL,11,Fseparate route for Palestinians to
OL,12,Fcome to the UK.
OL,14,FThe Hamas-run health ministry in Gaza
OL,15,Fsays more than 32,000 Palestinians
OL,16,Fhave now been killed by Israeli
OL,17,Fmilitary action, including around
OL,18,F13,000 children.
