OL,3,CGaza: British families call for
OL,4,CUkrainian-style visa scheme to get
OL,5,Crelatives out
OL,7,FCurrently, there is only one exit
OL,8,Froute out of Gaza via a crossing in
OL,9,Fthe southern city of Rafah, which has
OL,10,Falso become the latest target of
OL,11,FIsrael's campaign against Hamas.
OL,13,FOnly a few Palestinians have been
OL,14,Fallowed to evacuate to Egypt,
OL,16,FMs Abusalama tells ITV News she also
OL,17,Frecently paid "a lot of money" to get
OL,18,Fher immediate family out of Gaza.
