OL,3,CGaza: British families call for
OL,4,CUkrainian-style visa scheme to get
OL,5,Crelatives out
OL,7,FHer parents have since moved to Spain,
OL,8,Fwhere she visits to take care of them.
OL,9,FShe says she can't bring herself to
OL,10,Freturn to the UK at the moment.
OL,12,F"I had to get escape, it was
OL,13,Fsuffocating, it felt unsafe, and it
OL,14,Ffelt alienating. Spain has shown much
OL,15,Fmore humility in response to what is
OL,16,Fhappening in Gaza," she adds.
OL,18,FMs Abusalama was born and raised in
OL,19,FJabalia Refugee Camp, in northern Gaza
OL,20,Fbut came to the UK in 2014.
