OL,7,FThere, she completed her MA at SOAS
OL,8,Fand PhD at Sheffield Hallam
OL,9,FUniversity, where she also specialised
OL,10,Fand taught in media studies. She was
OL,11,Fgranted citizenship in June 2023.
OL,13,FHer local MP, Harriet Harman, whom Ms
OL,14,FAbusalama appealed to on numerous
OL,15,Foccasions has also not responded to
OL,16,FITV News' request for comment.
